{"tid":2430509,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔好放棄年青人」《狂舞派3》「狂」不了","createTime":"2021-03-03T03:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T03:11:35.000Z","uid":250039,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c740bfeebc0f376dc88433736a6011d911f50e","tid":2430509,"uid":250039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>《狂舞派3》（The Way We Keep Dancing）</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CL6WKSYHZYm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCL6WKSYHZYm%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiup4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=a7160718\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCL6WKSYHZYm%2F&h=4aa9ac3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CL6WKSYHZYm/</a><br />\n老實說，對港產片始終有一種難以捨割的感情，但看電影最重要不盲從附和，相信做一位港產片「最忠誠的反對派」就最適合不過了。先旨聲明，在沒有先過《狂舞派》之下去看《狂舞派3》（The Way We Keep Dancing），劇情脈絡大概看得通，完場散席時卻五味雜陳，為勢所迫的狂舞派好像再也「狂」不了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eatnplay.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/03235134/45556267_2049324758450047_138217880150867968_o-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eatnplay.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F03235134%2F45556267_2049324758450047_138217880150867968_o-1.jpg&h=52767f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《狂舞派3》很巧妙跳出續集框框，一來就是承接著電影世界內《狂舞派2》的上映，以Hana（顏卓靈飾）為首的一群Artists面對生存的各樣掙扎。《狂舞派3》的野心很大，先由主角們的個人層面出發，延伸到香港杜會林林總總問題，工廈、香港文化創作、加租、市區重建等等，一眾主角的「狂」都不得不回歸現實、理性，要搵食嘛，談何容易。《狂舞派3》亦不止於用上舞蹈，更加入了Hip Hop的元素。可惜本身應該貫穿全片的舞蹈只寥寥出現數幕，反而Hip Hop更承載全片的重心，令電影不禁有點顧此失彼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201125/408250746962710528569127.jpeg/5f5iWAdaywbn8NzAP6frbEGI27vsRvgXgFK_U4BSv1M?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201125%2F408250746962710528569127.jpeg%2F5f5iWAdaywbn8NzAP6frbEGI27vsRvgXgFK_U4BSv1M%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=bf75fe8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了宣傳之故，在上映前試當真上載了《狂舞派2》的短劇，當中黃修平的一句「唔好放棄年青人」不是信口開河，在《狂舞派3》切實拍出社會面對的問題、叩問年青人的將來。當中令人最感同身受的，可能不是一眾主角，而是飾演年輕記者的游學修就像現今的年青人，臉上總是掛著嬉皮笑臉，笑口噬噬，誰知跟Baby John坐下抽煙，即換上一副「老屎忽」姿態，慨嘆早心灰意冷，幸好有狂舞街這個題材，才不至辭職。縱然懷憂喪志有時，要祝福各位心理愉快，才可以繼續鬥命長，多出街。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ndl0hPu3u08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNdl0hPu3u08&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiup4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=fc4f2fe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ndl0hPu3u08</a><br />\n各位啱睇不妨俾個like，得閒睇完戲會打下文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/movies234.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmovies234.hk&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiup4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=f3d8d24b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/movies234.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/movies234.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmovies234.hk&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiup4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=8bcac67c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/movies234.hk</a>"},{"pid":"82fc6e4937de250cefbead3f6ae5b53ace842e19","tid":2430509,"uid":250039,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwrRmAuWzQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgwrRmAuWzQw&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiup4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=6d16dc44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwrRmAuWzQw</a><br />\n<br />\n既然黃修平都講得出「唔好放棄年青人」，咁觀眾們都唔好放棄港產片啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p